---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = "About";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} description="About this site.">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Kit Connect</h1>

    <p class="lead">
      Kit Connect is a personal blog about figure and model making, painting, and doll photography.
    </p>

    <p>
      Rather than focusing only on finished works,  
      this site also shares the creative process â€” including experiments, mistakes, and small discoveries along the way.
    </p>

    <h2>What you can find here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Figure and model build logs</li>
      <li>Painting notes and techniques</li>
      <li>Figure reviews</li>
      <li>Doll photography</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Everything is shared in a relaxed and casual way.
    </p>

    <h2>About the creator</h2>

<div class="about-author">
  <a
    href="https://x.com/kit_connect"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="about-author-link"
  >
    <img
      src="/images/profile/icon.avif"
      alt="Kit Connect creator icon"
      class="about-author-icon"
    />

    <p class="about-author-name">
      Kit Connect
    </p>
  </a>

  <div class="about-author-text">
    <p>
      I enjoy building and painting models as a personal hobby.  
      This site was created to document the process, not just the final results.
    </p>

    <p>
      If it inspires or encourages others who enjoy creative hobbies,  
      I would be very happy.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


    <h2>About image usage</h2>
    <p>
      All images on this site include a watermark to help prevent unintended reuse.
    </p>

    <p>
      Some images may be slightly harder to see,  
      but this is a small effort to keep the site comfortable and enjoyable as a personal hobby space.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please do not reuse or redistribute the images without permission.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
